CLEARMETHOD
PRERUNPROGRAM 0
POSTRUNPROGRAM 0
ENABLEACQUISITION 1
ENABLEANALYSIS 1
CUSTOMANALYSIS 0
COPYMETHOD 0
SAVEGLPDATA 0
PRERUNNAME ""
POSTRUNNAME ""
SIGNAL2METH ""
ANALYSISMACRO ""
METHODCOMMENT
METHODCOMMENT "Method to demo HP 6890 parameter editing for Split/Splitless & Cool On\"
METHODCOMMENT "-Column inlets plus NPD and ECD.  This method is for the purpose of OF\"
METHODCOMMENT "FLINE demos only!"
METHODCOMMENT ""
METHODCOMMENT "In order to load this method use the macro ""6890demo.mac"" or copy th\"
METHODCOMMENT "e file 'IQ1.MTH' from this methods' subdirectory to the instrument sub\"
METHODCOMMENT "directory and rename it 'IQ1.cfg'.  The method can then be loaded"
METHODCOMMENT "and will show appropriate parameters.\"
